          "body": "{\n    \"data\": [\n        {\n            \"id\": \"17943720849036478\",\n            \"caption\": \"Whether you’re running a backup generator for your factory, fueling a boat for the morning catch, or powering tractors on the farm, you need diesel access that is simple, safe, and reliable.\\n\\nWith ZipFuel’s robust 20L Jerry Cans, transporting High Speed Diesel has never been easier. Designed to meet strict government PESO standards, our tamper-resistant cans ensure that every drop you buy is safely transported to where you need it most.\\n\\nSecure your fuel. Secure your business. Ask for ZipFuel at your nearest participating pump today! 🛢️⚡\\n\\n#ZipFuel #AgricultureIndia #ConstructionIndia #GeneratorFuel #ReliablePower\",\n            \"media_type\": \"IMAGE\",\n            \"media_url\": \"https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/726539576_18186916855387181_7524206128950500402_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=106&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=H5E--8U24gcQ7kNvwFcljUs&_nc_oc=Ado-1C8dMEghjhc2_A7Kpk1I2CZeItvVw_3n52T_mxgyJravb-nF9fEe16vayhE-hrsIBCqvlWQsaENVy5DnHxkF&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=G7K4GKw-XY0lxbkmqo6ULA&oh=00_Af_e1N79SVwN9uok-eJDK6e9ZlP_nqgeFN4u-7C6WxqX0A&oe=6A3B7247\",\n            \"permalink\": \"https://www.instagram.com/p/DZuylANNaSo/\",\n            \"timestamp\": \"2026-06-18T14:47:26+0000\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"id\": \"18562375090071307\",\n            \"caption\": \"The recent government order banning fuel dispensing in non-PESO approved containers is here to keep us all safe, but it doesn’t mean your operations have to slow down.\\n\\nEnter ZipFuel. Our 20-litre, fully PESO-approved Jerry Cans are your legal, safe, and efficient ticket to keeping your generators, farm equipment, and worksites fully fueled.\\n\\n✅ 100% PESO-Approved\\n✅ Leak-Proof & Tamper-Resistant\\n✅ Built for Heavy-Duty Transport\\n\\nSwap out your old plastic cans today! Visit participating retail outlets and ask for ZipFuel.\",\n            \"media_type\": \"IMAGE\",\n            \"media_url\": \"https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/725742978_18186823981387181_2034298063033510702_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=Wp60H3i-XskQ7kNvwH7p9Mx&_nc_oc=AdprWFH3xhSSqbkv2x3wAgi_wqatg1FFuRkyWcF7ZYjMC46JqSB_UAIT3Maldt-yJYuc3NrqTwyXYCp5UVzNtiuh&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=G7K4GKw-XY0lxbkmqo6ULA&oh=00_Af8y4JqFX2pTmqSkzgumfbDTtNT2Sl68FxbCX25xajK_xw&oe=6A3B6ABD\",\n            \"permalink\": \"https://www.instagram.com/p/DZsb1ZPtd1e/\",\n            \"timestamp\": \"2026-06-17T16:50:01+0000\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"id\": \"18092651543575452\",\n            \"caption\": \"Long weekend road trips made easy. \\n\\nIn&Out convenience store enhances quick stops for snacks, drinks, fruits, and essentials. ​\\n\\nEverything you need in one place, so next time you\\nstop, fuel from BPCL & enjoy this convenience at its\\ncore. 🚗✨​\\n\\n#In&Outstore #Conevenience #BPCL #EnergisingLives​\",\n            \"media_type\": \"VIDEO\",\n            \"media_url\": \"https://instagram.fbho3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQMH1sX5UU3fX2I2vWGuL6j3uIbNwU1TxzS-1OkJIBZ2Ld1Eqp4cUE3yd5DyTp9gP8Zm9L1QgDpHZETP6bHxmASKFr_mLtP6DVH_KCs.mp4?_nc_cat=109&_nc_oc=AdqVbTDDyZz2Jmklx3DlBG9H2B1INmTSUgPjINlRujPucDtq_sPlQpnvbB31wPxoYFyGkkTJq5jZHAtcj2P6x1Y_&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=instagram.fbho3-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=-Erhqxb3gDoQ7kNvwGDDXop&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTI5MTUxNjExOTYzNTIyNywiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjMsInZpX3VzZWNhc2VfaWQiOjEwMDk5LCJkdXJhdGlvbl9zIjozMCwidXJsZ2VuX3NvdXJjZSI6Ind3dyJ9&ccb=17-1&vs=573ca0a36e1a5f39&_nc_&_nc_gid=G7K4GKw-XY0lxbkmqo6ULA&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_Af-pZb2fz